alluxio.collections

Class IndexDefinition<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.collections.IndexDefinition<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of objects in this IndexedSet

    @ThreadSafe
public abstract class IndexDefinition<T>
extends Object
    A class representing the definition of an index for this IndexedSet. Each instance of this class must implement the method to define how to get the value of the field chosen as the index key. Users use this indexDefinition class as the parameter in all methods of IndexedSet to represent an index.
